{
  "stem": "5357.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I was four years old in a few months, so I remember all these things very vividly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There wasn't enough food, and people were going around hungry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In a way, we were luckier than most of all, because my sister had a store.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she left all merchandise when she went to Warsaw, so we were selling the stuff.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, materials and curtain stuff and stockings and things like that for women.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were selling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my sister, Rachel, she really looked like a Polish girl with the nose and the blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she would go out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You see, our city had three ghettos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a big city, and somehow they made three ghettos from it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But at night, for curfew, they closed it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one couldn't visit the other one, because there was a space between each one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she was going to the Polish side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was buying stuff, selling and buying stuff.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember, myself, I used to climb through a wall-- maybe it was six feet or more, such a block wall-- to go to the Polish side and buy salt, sugar, potatoes, and some bread.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I would go through a special site.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, the thing is that in the ghetto you did not need Germans to watch it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had a post, an outpost, where trucks or wagons came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the rest was not guarded, because the Polish people were very good guard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they saw a Jew, they made sure that they turned them in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was a kid with long braids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we lived in another side of the city, so the people did not know me very well.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
